the city was told last week that it had been awarded a $500,000 grant to extend streets, water lines and sewer lines to the site
construction was to be completed by july to allow the plant to begin distribution of products purchased for the christmas season
brookstone's commitment represents a significant step in the growth of the mexico-area economy,'' said mexico mayor larry webber
brookstone officials said they selected mexico because of the available work force and the positive relationship city officials have with existing employers
brookstone offers tools, household items and automotive products. besides it's catalog sales operation, brookstone has 80 retail outlets in 26 states
